snippet.title: Mortal Kombat 1 – Official Peacemaker Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Eat peace, Motherfuckers!

Peacemaker comes to MK1 Early Access February 28, Full Release March 6. Janet Cage joins the Kameo roster later in March.

Get the Premium Edition or add the Kombat Pack to your Standard Edition to play as Peacemaker: https://www.mortalkombat.com/purchase

It's In Our Blood. Discover a reborn Mortal Kombat Universe created by Fire God Liu Kang. Mortal Kombat 1 ushers in a new era of the iconic franchise with a new fighting system, game modes, and Fatalities!
